Class ObjectSet

java.lang.Object
com.example.fitnesstracker.ObjectSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ObjectSet extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a set in a workout, consisting of the number of repetitions (reps) and the weight used.
